{
  "stem": "4284.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Consequently, the problems of registration with the police, which of course you never did anything to disturb that-- the only time that we had to go to the police was when Germany forced Jewish males to add the name Israel to the name and the Jewish women were forced to add Sarah to the name.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And since this has to become your legal name, you had to go to the police department and register.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And believe me, you went with a great deal of apprehension.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody can understand what it's like to go into a beehive of Nazi officials, especially police, and hopefully just be able to change your name and sign it and then walk out of it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One cannot understand the German mentality, what it is to officially, patriotically, as they would call it, hate and abuse Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anything they wanted to do, they got away with it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was no policemen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was no court.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was no judge, no Supreme Court that would uphold the rights.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On the contrary, you would see many times judges sitting in courts, and what they would display with a great deal of pride is the party pin, the party insignia, and there was no way that you could ever find justice.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So consequently, this Jewish service center provided us with information and with updates.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, of course, that's the place where you have to pick up the star.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could not pin that on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The reason was the Germans would assume that if you pinned it on, you could take it off and slide by a get by, as we would say, would pass as a non-Jew.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we have to have plenty of stars for the few clothing we had that we had to sew it on.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
